 148:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     When The compilation define USE_HAL_UART_REGISTER_CALLBACKS is set to 0 or
 149:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     not defined, the callback registration feature is not available
