 261:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****   Depending on the frame length defined by the M1 and M0 bits (7-bit,
 262:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****   8-bit or 9-bit), the possible UART formats are listed in the
 263:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****   following table.
 264:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c **** 
 265:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****   Table 1. UART frame format.
 266:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     +-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
 267:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |  M1 bit |  M0 bit |  PCE bit  |             UART frame                |
 268:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 269:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    0      |    | SB |    8 bit data   | STB |     |
 270:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 271:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    0    |    1      |    | SB | 7 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 272:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 273:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    1    |    0      |    | SB |    9 bit data   | STB |     |
 274:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 275:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    0    |    1    |    1      |    | SB | 8 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 276:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 277:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    1    |    0    |    0      |    | SB |    7 bit data   | STB |     |
 278:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 279:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     |    1    |    0    |    1      |    | SB | 6 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 280:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_uart.c ****     +-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
